{"tid":1173053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為創辦人任正非：若向Apple報復我第一個反對","createTime":"2019-05-27T00:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T02:47:18.000Z","uid":3090,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0562ad0ad4234b4a0e676bad1c9d708a989a0867","tid":1173053,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T00:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3AhZfX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3AhZfX.png&h=dcb3565d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n任正非在訪問中表明反對向美國蘋果公司報復。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n中國電訊設備生產商華為遭美國「封殺」，創辦人任正非周日接受彭博電視訪問時表示，若中國向美國蘋果公司(Apple）報復，他第一個反對。<br />\n<br />\n美國以國安為由針對華為，有人呼籲中國向蘋果公司報復，但任正非表示那不會發生，如果發生，他第一個反對。<br />\n<br />\n任正非大讚蘋果領導全球，指出沒有蘋果，就沒有手機互聯網；沒有蘋果協助展現世界，大家就看不到美好的世界。<br />\n<br />\n任正非形容蘋果是他的老師，比華為先進，反問身為學生的他，為何要反對老師。他說華為絕不會向蘋果報復。<br />\n<br />\n彭博網站"},{"pid":"c2884e321351af283080b0e75a5a25b557519546","tid":1173053,"uid":196924,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T00:21:13.000Z","msg":"反問身為學生的他，為何要反對老師。<br />\n<br />\n支狗咪就係呢種垃圾思想搞到自己on99咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老師話1+1=3係咪都唔會反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1ad5e29fb7c85e4feae19b2d042ea4d730758c","tid":1173053,"uid":224533,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T00:26:21.000Z","msg":"以為讚吓蘋果侵侵會手下留情？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6459de93dbfe1c65009b842e5c7589ff33bb953","tid":1173053,"uid":150347,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T00:26:33.000Z","msg":"對大陸人黎講，無得用Iphone慘過食2舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c4e1c017aaa0a8c1109bfd77eb0594b65d7e07","tid":1173053,"uid":176313,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T00:27:44.000Z","msg":"反apple 會俾囡囡屌架<img src=\"/asse